high_descs: Turn around to face the small white table.
Pick the knife up from off of the table.
Turn to the left and go towards the microwave on the white table in the corner.
Open the microwave, slice the potato, and close the microwave.
Continue to face the microwave on the white table.
Open the microwave, place the knife inside of it, and close the microwave.
Move slightly to the left.
Open the microwave, pick up the potato slice inside, close the microwave.
Turn around, go straight and then to the left to face the stove.
Place the potato slice in the pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn around, go straight, then go to the left to face the black refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the pan inside, and close the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Move the pan from the stove top to inside the black refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the white table with the chair and silverware and brown plate.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn to your left and walk to the white table with the microwave.
Open the microwave door, slice the potato on the inside left of the microwave, close the microwave door.
Move to stand in front of the right side of the microwave.
Open the microwave door and place the knife behind the apple on the plate in the microwave.
Close the microwave door, move to stand in front of the left side of the microwave.
Open the microwave door, pick up a slice from the potato, close the microwave door
Turn around and walk to the stove on the other side of the room.
Place the potato slice in the pan on the left front burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the potato slice in it by the handle.
Turn to your right and walk to the front of the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the pan on the right side of the top rack and close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, place a slice in a pan, refrigerate it

high_descs: go left to white square table
pick up knife from table
turn around, go to table with microwave
slice potato on left side of plate in microwave, close microwave
turn right toward window, turn left to face microwave
open microwave, place knife on plate in microwave, behind apple, close microwave
turn right, turn left to face microwave
open microwave, pick up apple slice in microwave, close microwave
turn around, go to stove to the left
place apple slice in square pan on stove
pick up square pan with apple slice from stove
turn around, go to refrigerator to the left
open refrigerator, place square pan on right side of top shelf of refrigerator, close refrigerator
anns.task_desc: Place apple slice in microwave, into square pan on stove, place pan in refrigerator
